{"tid":2037221,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黑色洋紫荊 icon在維基百科被提出刪除","createTime":"2020-05-27T01:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T11:21:46.000Z","uid":10540,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f3189d35a7444a05e311b698423a751d85d967e3","tid":2037221,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T01:04:32.000Z","msg":"一年前，文宣組巴打們做左個icon<br />\n<br />\n黑色洋紫荊 &mdash; 香港被毀，但香港人絕對可以令我城重生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KbgrA2D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKbgrA2D.png&h=6ee139a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過根據維基百科制度，要採用CC-BY-SA 4.0和PD授權先唔會就俾人刪</span></span>，所以大家一定要搵原作者出聲明支持用，先唔會俾人刪。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Flag_of_Hong_Kong_(Black_Bauhinia_with_wilted_petals_variant).svg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFile%3AFlag_of_Hong_Kong_%28Black_Bauhinia_with_wilted_petals_variant%29.svg&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8UwoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=8404c818\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Flag_of_Hong_Kong_(Black_Bauhinia_with_wilted_petals_variant).svg</a>"},{"pid":"2152f2558e6a7677c84e5e9f352267dfd3102866","tid":2037221,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T01:11:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69708ac4015b865933dad9e19da9d6de694d0a9c","tid":2037221,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T01:13:51.000Z","msg":"［互相配合］五毛：送頭，狗：人少左，方便拉人，逐個擊破<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2037201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2037201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"51d994afa5072dc3e748ee706686ae80b5b33b15","tid":2037221,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T01:14:22.000Z","msg":"要搵返原作者出嚟授權 <img src=\"/assets/faces/nor